			<h3 ><a href="#p114567">Re: XV-11 bumper design and climbing</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=114567&amp;sid=db14c9b53ecaf4bdb4905ec94b2a1e1c#p114567"><img src="./styles/robotreviews/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=19808&amp;sid=db14c9b53ecaf4bdb4905ec94b2a1e1c">glnc222</a></strong> &raquo; March 9th, 2013, 7:29 pm </p>

			

			<div class="content"><span style="font-weight: bold">pivoting plastic version</span><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment">
